{"tid":1047794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"百日咳肆虐 衞署籲孕婦打疫苗護嬰","createTime":"2019-03-05T07:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T06:07:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1a8a350624a3c5abd58a8a451f52a03f0ad1a3","tid":1047794,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190305/20626329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F20626329&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=795b2bd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F20626329&h=0a5fd9d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190305/20626329</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百日咳肆虐 衞署籲孕婦打疫苗護嬰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190305/large/05la6p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190305%2Flarge%2F05la6p11.jpg&h=413e122c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防護中心建議孕婦打無細胞型百日咳疫苗加強保護。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港去年錄得110宗百日咳個案，創21年新高。由於初生嬰兒要到六個月大才完成基本百日咳疫苗接種，衞生防護中心轄下疫苗可預防疾病科學委員會建議，懷孕婦女在懷孕期間要接種一劑無細胞型百日咳疫苗，為嬰兒提供直接保護。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署正與醫管局合作籌劃落實有關建議，詳情將適時公佈，惟是否資助免費打費、打針時間表等均未有交代。<br />\n<br />\n根據科學委員會建議，孕婦可在妊娠第二或三期期間任何時間打針，但在懷孕35周前接種為佳，因產生抗體需時約兩星期，始能由母體透過胎盤把抗體傳送給胎兒。<br />\n<br />\n中心建議，使用的疫苗應為「白喉（減量）、破傷風及無細胞型百日咳（減量）混合疫苗」（「dTap疫苗」），「白喉（減量）、破傷風、無細胞型百日咳（減量）及滅活小兒麻痹混合疫苗」（「dTap-IPV疫苗」）亦可使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嬰兒最易受感染<br />\n<br />\n孕婦現時建議每年接種當季滅活季節性流感疫苗，中心指可與含百日咳疫苗一同接種；若在孕期沒有接種百日咳疫苗，婦女在產後盡早接種疫苗，仍能為嬰兒提供間接保護，接種在出院前進行為佳。<br />\n<br />\n百日咳可影響所有年齡層人士，太年幼、未能接種疫苗的嬰兒最易受感染，且出現嚴重併發症機會較高，並可致命。本港自2017年百日咳個案大幅上升，由之前5年每年20至50宗，升至17年的69宗及18年的110宗。17及18年179宗個案中，約40%涉及6個月以下嬰兒，全部均未曾完成百日咳疫苗基礎接種，約20%更為兩個月以下的嬰兒，仍未適齡接種含百日咳的疫苗，故中心建議孕婦打針加強保護。<br />\n<br />\n■記者嚴敏慧  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n首個地區康健中心 建制組織中標<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n內地男偷香油錢囚四周"},{"pid":"4a2fc4d99fa6e1b5d1966d024d285361e7252fe8","tid":1047794,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"咁撚多大陸賤嬰死撚左又 WFC<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751ecb842ff1dab150749b7e6dbeb20bfbb756eb","tid":1047794,"uid":25424,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"呢D幾耐未見過嘅病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一撚定係啲支那人惹落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9711029264ab546ecec4d0d8ca441df91fa82c2c","tid":1047794,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"願祝所有大陸賤種新移民早日同毛魔團聚"},{"pid":"f1e68fcb8130fd7e1ae82d6c5583c093e000ebcc","tid":1047794,"uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"絕跡多年的病，因為港中融化而重現"},{"pid":"41d550270acf05e950222c833ea0ad89c32b0bce","tid":1047794,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"支那又帶埋啲香港少見疾病黎香港"},{"pid":"4da0b0469cd25d9a930d580ab68ed088e5730674","tid":1047794,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"唔差在落來生埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b881df6cac7dbf1290f61f44b89e05531db6214c","tid":1047794,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"假疫苗影響<br />\n百日咳幾十年前香港已經幾乎絕曬種<br />\n大陸雖然都強制打，但根本就無用，肺癆都係一樣道理<br />\n<br />\n有d大陸老母費事落香港打就會大陸打咗算，果d通常假疫苗黎，有無抗體香港係完全無check<br />\n<br />\n以前無呢個問題係因為舊時大陸用日本疫苗，而家唔用日本玩自主研發就瀨曬野"},{"pid":"d76e31800fce8585047e0ad183c28bd866210b4b","tid":1047794,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"洗腦第一步：反疫苗「資訊」如何雄霸網絡？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1046039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1046039</a><br />\n<br />\n（不盲從）美青年上國會指摘on 9 反疫苗父母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1050321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1050321</a><br />\n<br />\n美國都有on 9 反疫苗父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}